model.metaheuristic.solution

Interface Solution<Type>

  • Type Parameters:
    Type - The type that contains the solution.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGenericSolution, IntegerSolution, ObjectSolution, PointSolution

    public interface Solution<Type>
    Representation of the solution. It contain the result of objective function associated to his decision variables.
